events.title: Cal Invitational Speech and Debate Tournament
events.location: UC Berkeley (mix of in-person and online divisions)
events.description: Formal invitation to the 2026 Cal Invitational Speech and Debate Tournament, with a mix of speech and debate events. Specific event mix and online/in-person status TBD.

events.title: The Future of Autonomous Mobility: Agile and Collaborative Robot Autonomy (ITS Transportation Seminar)
events.organizer: Institute of Transportation Studies (ITS), UC Berkeley
events.description: Giuseppe Loianno, UC Berkeley Electrical Engineering and Computer Science Associate Professor, will present on agile and collaborative robot autonomy. Cookie Hour precedes the seminar at 2:30 p.m.

events.title: Rethinking Mobility: Human-Centered AI for Safe, Confident and Fun Driving (ITS Transportation Seminar)
events.organizer: Institute of Transportation Studies (ITS), UC Berkeley
events.description: Avinash Balachandran, VP of Human Interactive Driving at the Toyota Research Institute, will discuss human-centered AI for driving. Cookie Hour precedes the seminar at 2:30 p.m.

events.title: Traffic Safety Innovation Summit
events.organizer: Swedish-American Chamber of Commerce SF & Silicon Valley (hosted at UC Berkeley's Richmond Field Station)
events.description: A premier event hosted by the Swedish-American Chamber of Commerce SF & Silicon Valley focusing on traffic safety innovation, held at a UC Berkeley facility.
